{
  "texts": [
    "Clearly, none of the prompts resulted in completely correct extraction for the 10 Pennsylvania well records.",
    "For the location, Llama 2 70B model with the best-performing prompt (i.e., Prompt 4) resulted in an accuracy of 70%.",
    "This corresponded to 7 correctly extracted well locations.",
    "For the depth information extraction task, a value of 90% was achieved for AOS from all four prompts, indicating that we obtained correct depth information for 9 out of 10 documents.",
    "Two possible reasons may explain this performance."
  ]
}